version_description: Chords to sing along to. Heard by ear from the original track.
This version has more accurate chords.
More varied in chords and capo brings the tone up.
I think that these are the correct chords, in comparison to the other version, after playing these along with the song.
This version contains the correct version of hammer on and pull off, which I mentioned in earlier versions of the website and also added the chord progression for the fill after the second chorus.
